<Class name="CM_PreNote" id="413ebda7-30ca-48e9-a8b8-5a9163f3f27c">
    <superclass name="CM_Object"/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <abstract/>
    <text>
NOTE - THIS HAS BEEN SUPERCEEDED AND MOST NO LONGER APPLIES

A pre-notification of an interaction with the Port.

These are broken down into Receival and Release sub-classes.  2 classes (CM_OperatorPreNote and
CM_OperatorEmptyRelease) can cover a number of visits with the port (ie. receiving a number
of items or releasing a number of empty containers) without specification of the actual tracked
item ids.  The other classes (CM_ConsignorPreNote, CM_ImportPreNote, CM_EmptyPreNote) are for
actual visits by a carrier to the port.

Receival
--------
The shipping company enters a Booking Reference (CM_OperatorPreNote) which
specifies the number of containers the port will receive from a consignor
for a voyage.  The booking reference does not have a specific tracked item ID.

The consignor enters a pre-note (CM_ConsignorPreNote) when they have packed 
a container and are about to phyiscally send it to the port.  The pre-note
includes the details defaulted from the booking reference and a specific tracked
item ID (eg. container number).  The consignor will be issued with a PIN number
which can be used by the carrier at the gate to access the pre-note details.

Release
-------
Import Release (CM_ImportPreNote)
An external user can access the system and enter an imported container number which
is awaiting release.  They can enter import release details and receive a PIN number 
which can be used by the carrier at the gate to access the pre-note details.

Empty Release (CM_EmptyRelease)
Entered by (or on behalf of) the container operator to hold the details for a bulk
release of empty containers.  This does not usually include the container numbers
but the criteria to be released.

Empty Release PreNote (CM_EmptyPreNote)
Not yet implemented but will be so a carrier can access the system and receive a PIN
number for an empty release.</text>
    <DbClassMap file="prenotes"/>
